* Installation on Debian/Ubuntu:
  aptitue install xmonad xmonad-contrib
  # cabal install dbus? gnome-panel-devel? ...
* Installation on Mac 10.8:
  1. Install the haskell platform.
  2. cabal install xmonad xmonad-contrib --flags="-use_xft"
  3. cabal install xmobar --extra-lib-dirs=/opt/X11/lib --extra-include-dirs=/opt/X11/include
